<terms>
<item>
<title><code>Returns</code></title>
  <p>the <link xref="Cogl.PixelBuffer"/> that this
  buffer uses for storage. Note that if the bitmap was created with
  <link xref="Cogl.Bitmap.new_from_file"/> then it will not actually be using a
  pixel buffer and this function will return <code>null</code>.</p>
